title: Bonus: Ernie Paniccioli On Hip-Hop Legends + Charlotte Flair, WWE SmackDown Women's Champion
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Legendary photographer Ernie Paniccioli sits down with Ebro in the Morning to share some stories on how the beginning of his career, seeing the beginning and growth with hip hop, funny rare Notorious B.I.G. stories, Queen Latifah, Rakim & more! His book Hip Hop at the End of the World: The Photography of Brother Ernie is available now. 

SmackDown Women's Champion Charlotte Flair sits down with Ebro in the Morning to discuss her recent success, what's next for her, her opinion on Ronda Rousey, being the daughter of a legendary wrestler in Ric Flair, her thoughts on some superstars in the Women's Division and even addressed rumors of her future in the WWE. You can watch her live on the Road To Wrestlemania Saturday, March 5 at Madison Square Garden on Ticketmaster! 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
